item.title: Catfish
item.description: Chorus: Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah Verse 1: A smelly catfish Says "bongs away" Another golden day A smelly catfish Goes all the way Let's move out and play Now, the stench has hit it down on you Your nostrils feel the flu Now, the stench has pulled one on you An epidemic flu But say yeah, say yeah, say yeah if you don't care Chorus: Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah Verse 2: Smelly catfish You're going down I'll help you hit the ground Smelly catfish You make me frown Let's take away your crown See, the end is near, it's coming soon Get ready for your doom See, the end is clear, it's coming soon Bow down and face your doom And say yeah, say yeah, say yeah like you don't care Chorus: Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah Bridge: It’s too stinky, too stinky, too stinky in here… Chorus: Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, Yeah, oh, oh, oh, oh, Oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah
